# Castle Of The Winds Core Rules

- Read `AGENTS.md` and `docs/ai/PROJECT_BRIEF.md` before large changes.
- Runtime source of truth is `src/`.
- `app.js` is generated by `npm run build`; do not use it as the primary edit target.
- Keep changes in the smallest owning module.
- Preserve the current dependency-light architecture. Do not introduce frameworks or new build systems unless explicitly requested.
- Preserve mobile-first UX, touch controls, controller flows, and existing DOM/action hooks unless the task explicitly changes them.
- If you add a runtime module, update `scripts/build-app.mjs`.
- If save shape changes, update `src/features/persistence.js` migration logic.
- Prefer verification that matches the change: `npm run build`, `npm run test:rules`, `npm run playtest:harness`.
